  "blogContent": {
    "id": "198277446",
    "topics": [
      "LLM",
      "Halusinasi"
    ],
    "title": "Chain-of-Verification Mengurangi Halusinasi dalam Model Bahasa Besar",
    "slug": "chain-of-verification-reduces-hallucination-in-large-language-models",
    "authorName": "Prof. Otto Nomos",
    "authorPicture": {
      "url": "https://www.datocms-assets.com/101962/1692842125-profottonomosheadshot.png"
    },
    "_publishedAt": "2024-05-24T05:21:05+01:00",
    "description": "Komentar & Penilaian Abstrak",
    "thumbnail": {
      "url": "https://www.datocms-assets.com/101962/1692843326-researchpaper9.png"
    },
    "contentBlock": [
      {
        "mainContent": {
          "value": {
            "schema": "dast",
            "document": {
              "type": "root",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "span",
                      "value": "Diterbitkan pada 20 Sep"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "span",
                      "value": "Penulis:"
                    },
                    {
                      "url": "https://huggingface.co/shehzaadzd",
                      "type": "link",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "span",
                          "value": "Shehzaad Dhuliawala"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "span",
                      "value": ",Mojtaba Komeili,Jing Xu,"
                    },
                    {
                      "url": "https://huggingface.co/rraileanu",
                      "type": "link",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "span",
                          "value": "Roberta Raileanu"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "span",
                      "value": ",Xian Li,Asli Celikyilmaz,"
                    },
                    {
                      "url": "https://huggingface.co/spermwhale",
                      "type": "link",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "span",
                          "value": "Jason Weston"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "heading",
                  "level": 2,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "span",
                      "value": "Abstrak"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "span",
                      "value": "Generasi informasi faktual yang masuk akal namun salah, yang disebut halusinasi, adalah masalah yang belum terpecahkan dalam model bahasa besar. Kami mempelajari kemampuan model bahasa untuk mempertimbangkan kembali tanggapan yang mereka berikan untuk memperbaiki kesalahan mereka. Kami mengembangkan metode Chain-of-Verification (CoVe) di mana model pertama (i) menyusun tanggapan awal; kemudian (ii) merencanakan pertanyaan verifikasi untuk memeriksa fakta drafnya; (iii) menjawab pertanyaan-pertanyaan tersebut secara independen sehingga jawabannya tidak bias oleh tanggapan lain; dan (iv) menghasilkan tanggapan akhir yang diverifikasi. Dalam eksperimen, kami menunjukkan CoVe mengurangi halusinasi di berbagai tugas, dari pertanyaan berbasis daftar dari Wikidata, MultiSpanQA buku tertutup, dan generasi teks panjang."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "url": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2309.11495",
                      "meta": [
                        {
                          "id": "rel",
                          "value": "noreferrer"
                        },
                        {
                          "id": "target",
                          "value": "_blank"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type": "link",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "span",
                          "value": "Lihat halaman arXiv"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "url": "https://arxiv.org/pdf/2309.11495",
                      "meta": [
                        {
                          "id": "rel",
                          "value": "noreferrer"
                        },
                        {
                          "id": "target",
                          "value": "_blank"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type": "link",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "span",
                          "value": "Lihat PDF"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "heading",
                  "level": 2,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "span",
                      "value": "Komentar"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "span",
                      "value": "Makalah berjudul \"Chain-of-Verification Mengurangi Halusinasi dalam Model Bahasa Besar\" menangani masalah penting dalam model bahasa besar: generasi informasi yang masuk akal namun salah, yang dikenal sebagai halusinasi. Solusi yang diusulkan adalah metode yang disebut Chain-of-Verification (CoVe)."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "span",
                      "value": "Poin Utama:"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "list",
                  "style": "numbered",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "listItem",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "type": "span",
                              "marks": [
                                "strong"
                              ],
                              "value": "Masalah Halusinasi"
                            },
